data.description: Are you planning to build your dream home? Look no further! This property offers over a quarter acre of land, providing ample space to bring your ideas to life. Most of the basic details are already taken care of, so you can focus on adding your personal touches and making it your own. New electrical, plumbing, HVAC, furnace, drywall, and windows. With a little imagination and creativity, you can transform this property into your perfect home.No sign in the yard. Seller has relation to listing agent.
